## Implementation

- Converted terminal authorization-code exchange failures (`invalid_grant`, used/expired code, PKCE failure) into actionable retry guidance: restart with `/mcp auth-start <server>`.
- Cleared access/refresh token fields and PKCE verifier on rejected authorization-code exchange so no partial credential is left behind.
- Converted auth-required MCP tool execution failures into fast `AuthError` guidance naming the headless flow: run `senpi` interactive, `/mcp auth-start <server>`, then `/mcp auth-complete <server> <redirect-url>`.
- Added focused regressions for real tool execution without UI and one-use pasted code replay.

